      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the pedicle screw shank and rod junction. QoI (peak von Mises stress at critical cross-section) changed by 1.1% between medium and fine meshes. GCI = 2.8%. Final mesh selected at medium refinement level for computational efficiency."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
