    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against required level 3 due to single test condition; this shortfall is accepted given medium model risk, medium decision consequence, and the availability of corroborating analytical evidence. All three primary QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
